SummaryEnglish: Ren returns to his hometown with no memories of having lived there. When a a cell phone repairman installs the Monster Strike app on his phone, Ren finds himself pulled into a real-world version of the game and begins piecing his memories together again.
Aliases: モンスターストライク THE MOVIE はじまりの場所へ
Monster Strike The Movie: To The Place of Beginnings
